snippet.title: Aleph 0
snippet.description:
Thanks for stopping by! Aleph 0 is a channel devoted to bringing pure mathematics into the hands of learners. So far, this channel has videos on topology, algebraic geometry, PDEs, differential geometry, number theory, and more. If you're excited by pure math, or even if you're just curious about what it is, then you're in the right place.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/00aleph00
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/00aleph00
